      "description": "Wagotabi is your daily companion for learning Japanese from scratch, at your own pace, and with maximum immersion. Learn to read, write, and understand Japanese in context, while retaining Hiragana, Katakana, and Kanji. Use your knowledge directly in context, by interacting with locals, and using Japanese in daily situations.\nDiscover real Japanese cities and culture while going on a quest to become a Japanese Grand Master. \n\n\nDesigned in close collaboration with +300 Japanese language experts, official Japanese prefecture tourist associations and thousands of early testers, Wagotabi provides you with an immersive approach to language learning following a graded reader approach. Words and grammar points are introduced according to the JLPT standard, beginning with N5.\n\n—\n\n◆ START from zero: the game is beginner friendly: no initial Japanese knowledge needed. Concepts are introduced step by step and used right away in-game. Non-beginners will progress faster and equally enjoy the game.\n◆ JOURNEY in Japan: Explore real cities, learn to introduce yourself, order food, ask your way to the locals and unravel hidden secrets!\n◆ COLLECT new words, Kana, Kanji and get detailed explanations on grammar patterns and conjugation step-by-step. No more overwhelming Kana / Kanji / vocabulary lists.\n◆ CHALLENGE Japanese Grand Masters in their castle to earn their respect!\n◆ COMPETE with fellow learners on Kana and Kanji minigames and post your top scores to the leaderboard!\n◆ PERSONALIZE your learning experience: benefit from our SRS tool pin-pointing your weaknesses, create your own avatar, set the game difficulty. This is your Japanese journey.\n◆ ENJOY a fully ad-free experience without in-app purchase, the game can be entirely played offline!\n\n—\n\n(Non-exhaustive) list of features :\nInteractive dictionary (with illustrations, tags etc.), clear grammar explanation, interactive tooltips, fully voiced in Japanese, SRS powered smart tests, interactions with environment, quests, 2 minigames (Kana and Kanji), boss fights, Hiragana / Katakana / Kanji stroke order and calligraphy, Kanjidex, resembling Kanji, conjugation, cloud save, advanced progress tracking tools …\n\n—\n\nCurrently available content:\n+320 carefully selected words and grammar points   \n+165 Kanji  \n+450 example sentences  \n+1700 voiced Japanese dialogues  \n+300 unique NPCs in game  \nAll words / grammar are used extensively and in context for better retention\n\n—\n\nWhat our early testers are saying about Wagotabi:\n\"You guys are a blessing to bring this to the learning market!\"\n\"I have been using some of the App's examples for my lessons and my students are responding to them really well.\"\n\"I don't have the budget to travel to Japan, however I'm totally immersed in this game, learning effectively and witnessing my progress daily.\"\n\"Thanks to this app, my kids are now self-motivated to learn Japanese and reconnect with their roots. This concept is so Kawaii!“\n\"I'm preparing a trip to Japan and will definitely go check these spots I already visited in-game.\" \n\n—\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://www.wagotabi.com/privacy-policy\nTerms of Service: https://www.wagotabi.com/terms-of-service",
